<p style=3D"margin:0cm">Dear Sirs<o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm">Our Client:&nbsp;&nbsp;Mr Lee Hirst<o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm">Our Client's Vehicle:&nbsp;FORD KUGA TITANIUM TDCI<=
o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm">Registration:&nbsp;&nbsp;CE18FOM<o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm">Date of Accident:&nbsp;9 July 2026<o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">&nb=
sp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p align=3D"center" style=3D"margin:0cm;text-align:center"><b><u>Triage Onl=
y Request</u></b><o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">&nb=
sp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Ple=
ase find attached our client's images.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">&nb=
sp;<o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Ple=
ase will you provide an initial assessment to confirm if this vehicle is ro=
adworthy and repairable as soon as possible.&nbsp; We will forward the offi=
cial inspection instruction as soon as
 we are able.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p style=3D"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">&nb=
sp;<o:p></o:p></p>
