</td>
<td width=3D"434" valign=3D"top" style=3D"width:325.4pt;border-top:solid bl=
ack 1.0pt;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-righ=
t:solid black 1.0pt;padding:0cm 5.05pt 0cm 5.05pt">
<p style=3D"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">Our=
 client was stationary in their car on Lutterworth Road in Nuneaton for app=
roximately two seconds, while waiting to turn into Ivanhoe Avenue. Your ins=
ured was travelling directly behind
 our client and failed to come to a complete stop, and subsequently collide=
d with the rear of our client's stationary vehicle.<o:p></o:p></p>
</td>
</tr>
